description: Try our easy to follow Ocean Trout with Cajun Spices recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Fish dishes,Pescatarian,Low saturated fat,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Zucchini,High protein,High fibre,Wheat free,Quick & easy lunch,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Ocean Trout with Cajun Spices Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Spray fish with oil spray and sprinkle skinless side with spice.
Heat a non-stick frying pan over a medium-high heat and when hot spray with oil.
Cook fish skin-side down for 3 minutes, then turn over and cook for 2-3 minutes more or to your liking.
Remove from pan and keep warm.
Cut kernels from corn cob and add to pan. Cook for 2 minutes until tender. Add capsicum, zucchini and shallots and toss over heat until warmed through.
Place fish onto serving plates, top with warm salsa and coriander leaves.
Serve with mixed leaves and tartar sauce.
